Image Coordinates Transformation According to the Origin¶

Problem Statement¶

To find the coordinates of Point-1, Point-2 with respect to the Origin-2.

Given:¶

Coordinates of Point-1 (180, 185) and Point-2 (280, 120) with respect to Origin-1.
Coordinates of Origin-1 (314, 233) with Orgin-2.
